Spatulas were commonly used as cookware across the [[Realms]].{{Cite organized play/LC/How Long Can You Tread Water?|12}}{{Cite organized play/LC/Aethalynmur's Wings/Certificates}} 

In [[Wa]], a special metal-tipped osaye could be used to serve powdered [[incense]] during an incense ceremony.

Spatulas were also used as a tool for spreading non-food pastes and [[plaster]]s, similar to [[trowel]]s.
